election_record.label: Vermont 1816 Council

overview.note: The Original Election Returns tally sheet of aggregate vote totals lists 17026 votes for Joel Doolittle, 17021 votes for Ezra Butler, 17026 votes for Pliney Smith, 17021 votes for William Cahoon, 17020 votes for Timothy Stanley, 17023 votes for Josiah Wright, 17012 votes for Truman Chittenden, 17011 votes for Daniel Peaslee, 16999 votes for Thomas Hammond, 16853 votes for Theophilus Crawford, 16961 votes for Elias Keyes, 16877 votes for Frederick Bliss, 14028 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 14073 votes for Moses Robinson, 14017 votes for Nathaniel Chipman, 14019 votes for Josiah Hubbard, 14006 votes for Zebina Curtis, 13994 votes for Jonas Mann and 14172 votes for Solomon Miller.

North Star (Danville, VT), The Vermont Republican (Windsor, VT) and The National Standard (Middlebury, VT) report 17026 votes for Joel Doolittle, 17031 votes for Ezra Butler, 17026 votes for Pliney Smith, 17021 votes for William Cahoon, 17020 votes for Timothy Stanley, 17023 votes for Josiah Wright, 17013 votes for Truman Chittenden, 17011 votes for Daniel Peaslee, 16999 votes for Thomas Hammond, 16961 votes for Elias Keyes, 16877 votes for Frederick Bliss, 14028 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 14073 votes for Moses Robinson, 14017 votes for Nathaniel Chipman, 14019 votes for Josiah Hubbard, 14006 votes for Zebina Curtis, 13953 votes for John W. Chandler, 14020 votes for Zerah Willoby, 13997 votes for Denison Smith, 14009 votes for Daniel Dana, 13927 votes for Benjamin Wooster and 14172 votes for Solomon Miller.
North Star (Danville, VT) and The Vermont Republican (Windsor, VT) report 16853 votes for Theophilus Crawford.
The National Standard (Middlebury, VT) reports 16858 votes for Theophilus Crawford.
North Star (Danville, VT) reports 13991 votes for Jonas Mann.
The Vermont Republican (Windsor, VT) and The National Standard (Middlebury, VT) report 13994 votes for Jonas Mann.

sub_unit.name: Bridport
sub_unit.note: On the Original Election Returns tally sheet, no votes were given to Theophilus Crawford and 146 votes were given to the name Theophilus Harrington. This appears to be a transcription error, so these votes have been added to the total for Theophilus Crawford.
